						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/zdf-tv-interview-emaf.html" title="Permalink to ZDF TV interview at EMAF" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">ZDF</span> <span class="caps">TV</span> interview at <span class="caps">EMAF</span></a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/zdf-tv-interview-emaf.html" title="19:08" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-05-05T19:08:49+00:00" pubdate>May 5, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/zdf-tv-interview-emaf.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is an inter­view I did for Ger­man national <span class="caps">TV</span>, <span class="caps">ZDF</span>, while speak­ing at the European Media Art Fest­ival in Osnab­rueck in April:</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/zdfkulturzeit.jpg" alt="zdfkulturzeit" width="708" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3819" data-source="vimeo" data-id="93311172" /></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/93311172"><span class="caps">ZDF</span> Kul­turzeit inter­view about <span class="caps">EMAF</span></a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
