				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cinepolitics" rel="tag">Cinepolitics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/film-2" rel="tag">film</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/guantanamo" rel="tag">Guantanamo</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/interview" rel="tag">interview</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/press-tv" rel="tag">Press TV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/secrecy" rel="tag">secrecy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/tv" rel="tag">TV</a>			</span>
						
