	<article id="post-208" class="post-208 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-art-and-culture category-film category-intelligence category-interviews category-media category-radio category-spies category-uncategorized tag-dean-puckett tag-elephant-in-the-room tag-iops tag-intelligence-2 tag-media-2 tag-radio-2 tag-spies-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2008/08/bbc-radio-bristol-intervi.html" title="Permalink to BBC Radio Bristol Interview" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">BBC</span> Radio Bristol Interview</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2008/08/bbc-radio-bristol-intervi.html" title="16:36" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2008-08-30T16:36:04+00:00" pubdate>August 30, 2008</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2008/08/bbc-radio-bristol-intervi.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2008/08/bbc-radio-bristol-intervi.html/elephant" rel="attachment wp-att-865"><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/elephant.jpg" alt="" title="elephant" width="100" height="149" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-865" /></a>A recent <a href="http://www.indymedia.org.uk/media/2008/07//402836.mp3">inter­view</a> on <span class="caps">BBC</span> Radio Bris­tol to pub­li­cise the screen­ing of an award-winning new doc­u­ment­ary called <a href="http://www.facebook.com/group.php?gid=10962741034">“The Ele­phant in the Room”</a>, made by tal­en­ted dir­ector <a href="http://deaddeanfilms.com/">Dean Puck­ett</a>.</p>
<p>I had the chance to explore the mech­an­isms by which the <span class="caps">UK</span> media is con­trolled by the spies and the gov­ern­ment, includ­ing the sec­tion in <span class="caps">MI6</span> called I/Ops, which plants false stor­ies in the media to the bene­fit of <span class="caps">MI5</span> and <span class="caps">MI6</span>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2008/08/bbc-radio-bristol-intervi.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/art-and-culture" title="View all posts in Art &amp; Culture" rel="category tag">Art &amp; Culture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/film" title="View all posts in Film" rel="category tag">Film</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/interviews" title="View all posts in Interviews" rel="category tag">Interviews</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/media" title="View all posts in Media" rel="category tag">Media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/radio" title="View all posts in Radio" rel="category tag">Radio</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/uncategorized" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
