				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/dean-puckett" rel="tag">Dean Puckett</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/elephant-in-the-room" rel="tag">Elephant in the Room</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/iops" rel="tag">I/Ops</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/media-2" rel="tag">media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/radio-2" rel="tag">radio</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>			</span>
						
