				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/art" rel="tag">art</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/codes" rel="tag">codes</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/language" rel="tag">language</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/paul-flack" rel="tag">Paul Flack</a>			</span>
						
